Telkom has launched new FreeMe prepaid bundles as part of its new Summer promotion. The bundles include mobile data, WhatsApp data, SMSs, Telkom call minutes, and YouTube data. Telkom said the prepaid promotion will run from 20 September to 20 January 2019, and that terms and conditions apply. The table below details the new prepaid FreeMe bundles, with the terms and conditions explained below it. Telkom added that the 5GB, 10GB, and 20GB bundles receive up to “100+ hours” of free YouTube streaming, while the 20GB bundle also receives 1,500 call minutes to any network – excluding premium-rated numbers. An out-of-bundle rate of R0.30 per MB applies to all the bundles, while the YouTube streaming allocation is valid for one week only. <span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">﻿</span>